import React from 'react'
import { CardsContainer, Container, Card,Grow, Icon, Label, Media, Numbers, Title } from './style'

function OverviewSection() {
    return (
        <Container className ='container'>
            <Title>Overview - Today</Title>
            <CardsContainer>
                <Card>
                    <Media>
                        <Label>
                            Page Views
                        </Label>
                        <Icon/>
                    </Media>
                    <Numbers>
                        <Quantity>87</Quantity>
                        <Grow>3%</Grow>
                    </Numbers>
                </Card>
            </CardsContainer>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default OverviewSection
